

Cactus Code Thorn FLRWBackground
Thorn Author(s)      : Jordi Manyer <jfuertes7@physics.gatech.edu>
Thorn Maintainer(s)  : Jordi Manyer <jfuertes7@physics.gatech.edu>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

Provides initial FLRW background conditions for the thorns ADMBase and
HydroBase.

Provides FLRW boundary conditions for thorn GRHydro
Provides FLRW boundary conditions for thorn Kranc2BSSNChiMatter
